REST-PROJECT:

____________________________

rest-client:

AngularJs
auth: Basic (not secure)
almost no validation
main aim of the project was to expose REST endpoints and use them

____________________________

eve-python-rest:

simple REST server working with MongoDB

____________________________

mongodb:	sudo service mongod stop; mongod --dbpath={{path_to}}/rest-eve-python/data/db/
gui:		robomongo 		// from proper dir
server:		python api.py
angular:	grunt serve		// just for development
db manager:	mongo			// console mongoDB manager 


